information: Production of ecological lavander and lavandin flowers in 40 hectares . Distillation of the flowers in our own distilleries. The fields and the distilleries are in the natural park of las hoces del cabriel near valencia. All the process is controlled by the committee of ecological agriculture of the vallencia community (caecv)
